      "text": "questioned at least two of the witnesses.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "I am also aware of similar past cases. The color",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "photographs taken at Grand Blanc, Michigan by Joe Perry,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "amateur astronomer, on February 13, 1960 is one such case.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "After notifying the Air Force he was referred to the FBI and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "an investigation was conducted by two agents from the Flint",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "office. The photographs were subsequently furnished to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "the Air Force for analysis.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "What is the FBI's policy with respect to this matter",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "of investigation of such cases? Is there an official FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "regulation pertaining to FBI UFO investigatory policy, and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
